title: Follow live: Hawks, Magic battle for spot in NBA playoffs
Dolphins trying to trade star CB Ramsey, GM says
description: The Dolphins are having trade talks with other NFL teams about star cornerback Jalen Ramsey, general manager Chris Grier confirmed Tuesday.
author: Marcel Louis-Jacques

title: 'Despair for Emery, but Villa showed they belong'
description: Aston Villa fell short against PSG - but Unai Emery's side showed they now belong in this elite company, writes Phil McNulty.

title: Dart apologises for asking Boisson to 'put on deodorant'
description: British number four Harriet Dart apologises after asking the umpire to tell her opponent to put on deodorant during her first-round loss at the Rouen Open.

title: Arteta: Arsenal have no fear of Real Madrid as Raya insists: 'We will play to win'
description: Arsenal have no fear of facing Real Madrid at the Bernabeu and will play to win the game despite already holding a 3-0 advantage from the first leg, according to Mikel Arteta.

title: Can McIlroy win all four majors in 2025? 'The monkey is off his back'
description: Rory McIlroy suffered through 10 barren years at major tournaments before his stunning Masters triumph on Sunday clinched a career Grand Slam - and immediately raised the question of what will he achieve next?

title: Just one Ohio State player among 17 invited to 2025 NFL draft
description: Ohio State offensive tackle Josh Simmons one of 17 players invited to attend 2025 NFL draft in the green room.

title: Two UNC WBB stars earn WNBA Training Camp Invites
description: UNC WBB stars Alyssa Ustby and Maria Gakdeng didn't get selected in the WNBA Draft, but both are heading to separate teams via Training Camp Invites.
